{"tid":1550934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益：大家有咩問題想記者朋友係4點鐘記招問架？","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T02:28:03.000Z","uid":233229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d0badeb28d2ab718cfcfc537681475279589a9cd","tid":1550934,"uid":233229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"日日都例行記招相信大家都有好多問題想問下一班popo, 不如集思廣益下交啲問題比班記者朋友呀？<br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n<br />\n1. 今日/琴日 9月7號點解係大埔墟要打啲已經被popo推左埋鐵閘嘅小朋友？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2435720179846921?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2435720179846921%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=f103f3dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2435720179846921?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 今日/琴日 9月7號點解要1x個圍打一個走緊嘅人而打到爆頭？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/127810178561773?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F127810178561773%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=a8218ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/127810178561773?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 以下呢條片入面個popo癲左咁連續「警告」，究竟「警告」係點用架呢？中間有無需要比「被警告人士」作回應呢？<br />\n4. 又話會注意言詞，咁仲叫市民做「曱甴」？究竟啲記招講完會檢討，個進度係點呢？啲內部指引有無出到呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3190309980996194?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207097505984138%2Fposts%2F3190309980996194%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=8e113aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3190309980996194?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他？"},{"pid":"15e439e55bb1c6da09cfcd9d451bc53b714397f0","tid":1550934,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:49:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58b83e44a0a617397491b71b39f86aaf5c578d9a","tid":1550934,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:50:11.000Z","msg":"[置頂]20190908邊個衝美領就係鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2dd615f2ddc2b727aa2335afcd4cb37b722b929a","tid":1550934,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:50:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c9394d673e6cc8e5476ee375c30786bf748c8bd","tid":1550934,"uid":233229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:55:58.000Z","msg":"推呀呀呀"},{"pid":"1c336407985b54f1647a17c7406d8b9133e7c8f5","tid":1550934,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"對記者懷惡意<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1550779/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1550779/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"99431d0ac3d93eabee13f206cd46f90d2f616b9c","tid":1550934,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T1